.TH XCLBINUTIL "1" "October 2025" "xclbinutil        XRT Build Version: 2.21.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
xclbinutil \- manual page for xclbinutil        XRT Build Version: 2.21.0
.SH DESCRIPTION
This utility operates on a xclbin produced by v++.
.SS "For example:"
.TP
1) Reporting xclbin information
: xclbinutil \fB\-\-info\fR \fB\-\-input\fR binary_container_1.xclbin
.IP
2) Extracting the bitstream image: xclbinutil \fB\-\-dump\-section\fR BITSTREAM:RAW:bitstream.bit \fB\-\-input\fR binary_container_1.xclbin
3) Extracting the build metadata : xclbinutil \fB\-\-dump\-section\fR BUILD_METADATA:HTML:buildMetadata.json \fB\-\-input\fR binary_container_1.xclbin
4) Removing a section            : xclbinutil \fB\-\-remove\-section\fR BITSTREAM \fB\-\-input\fR binary_container_1.xclbin \fB\-\-output\fR binary_container_modified.xclbin
5) Signing xclbin                : xclbinutil \fB\-\-private\-key\fR key.priv \fB\-\-certificate\fR cert.pem \fB\-\-input\fR binary_container_1.xclbin \fB\-\-output\fR signed.xclbin
.PP
